🎮 Number Guessing Game
A simple Python game where you guess a number between 1 and 100!

🔹 How to Play
Run the game:
python guess_the_number.py

Select a difficulty:
Easy → 10 attempts
Hard → 5 attempts
Keep guessing until you find the correct number or run out of attempts.

🛠 Requirements
Python 3.x

Have fun guessing! 🎯
